 10    async def max_hitpoints(self) -> int:
 11        """
 12        Client's max hitpoints; base + bonus
 13        """
 14        base = await self.base_hitpoints()
 15        bonus = await self.bonus_hitpoints()
 16        return base + bonus
 17
 18    async def max_mana(self) -> int:
 19        """
 20        Clients's max mana; base + bonus
 21        """
 22        base = await self.base_mana()
 23        bonus = await self.bonus_mana()
 24        return base + bonus
